                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d299">
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Pringle</persName> to Mr. <persName
                            type="to">Gresham</persName>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Guatemala</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1894-03-10">
                            <hi rend="italic">March 10, 1894</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>U. S. consul at Tegucigalpa telegraphs that Americans who fought with Vasquez are
                    threatened with expulsion by President Bonilla. Consul Peterson urges my going
                    there on the <hi rend="italic">Ranger</hi>. Future complications might be
                    avoided by a strong protest.</p>
            </div>
        </body>
